The '''Royal Steward''' is an unnamed recurring character in ''[[Game of Thrones]]''. He is played by guest star [[Robert Sterne]] and debuts in &quot;[[Lord Snow]].&quot; The Royal Steward serves [[Iron Throne]]. He issues his summons and announces arrivals to the court.

sections.Biography:
===[[Season 1]]===
He summons the new [[Hand of the King]] [[Eddard Stark]] to the [[small council]] on his arrival in [[King's Landing]].&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Lord Snow]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt; He summons Eddard again when King [[Robert Baratheon]] receives news of [[Daenerys Targaryen]]'s pregnancy.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The Wolf and the Lion]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

He summons [[Eddard Stark]] to see the newly crowned King [[Joffrey Baratheon]] following the death of Robert in a hunting accident. Eddard is arrested and imprisoned when he impugns Joffrey's claim to the throne.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[You Win or You Die]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt; He announces the arrival of [[Sansa Stark]] to the court to plead mercy for her father.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The Pointy End]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
